profile_positions.description:
Researcher on public-private information infrastructures; Living Lab coordinator; and Teacher in BSc and MSc programmes at the Faculty of Technology, Policy and Management of Delft University of Technology. 

Main research activities: 
- Public-private governance research and coordinator of Living Labs in CASSANDRA;
- Research on new information and governance models for a Dutch Extended Single Window for trade;
- Research and community building in the eGovPoliNet project
